H0.text: Which company were responsible for the production of the Spitfire. Rolls-Royce

H1.text: Which company were responsible for the production of the Spitfire. de Havilland

H2.text: Which company were responsible for the production of the Spitfire. Hawker Aircraft

H3.text: Which company were responsible for the production of the Spitfire. Supermarine

A4.text: Full-scale production of the Spitfire began at Supermarine's facility in Woolston.

A5.text: The first production Spitfire, K9787, did not roll off the Woolston, Southampton assembly line until mid-1938.
